{"tid":2244104,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男警買K仔 藏毒罪成還柙候判","createTime":"2020-10-15T08:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T12:56:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"28e018567c59f51c4b6bbf41a31f82059bd72477","tid":2244104,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"男警休班期間在住所屋苑平台向毒販購買K仔，全程被刑事情報科同袍監視。毒販早已認罪判監，休班警及與毒販同行女子分別被控藏毒及販毒，兩人早前不認罪受審。裁判官今裁定男警稱落街打機及問路之說不可信，裁定他藏毒罪成，惟女被告沒參與毒品交收過程，獲判無罪。男警須還柙至本月30日判刑，裁判官表明，被告是警務人員，故拒索取感化或社會服務令報告，只索閱背景及戒毒所報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201015/XE4CGURVGJDOLNXVSXTYBEI4JI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201015%2FXE4CGURVGJDOLNXVSXTYBEI4JI%2F&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=7336d629\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201015%2FXE4CGURVGJDOLNXVSXTYBEI4JI%2F&h=8b668bde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201015/XE4CGURVGJDOLNXVSXTYBEI4JI/</a>"},{"pid":"a4f9f206f3467abfca6bbf1042c7aab31539f954","tid":2244104,"uid":76804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:51:43.000Z","msg":"件狗女呢<br />\n今次無律政司攬呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12d98829164aec950621b5d2e47ed4d2c0e48ad","tid":2244104,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4f9f206f3467abfca6bbf1042c7aab31539f954","tid":2244104,"uid":76804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:51:43.000Z","msg":"件狗女呢<br />\n今次無律政司攬呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:52:08.000Z","msg":"都冇狗閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔保啦"},{"pid":"e6f6a0bc8962daa7a2af8fadc0d56ecea3a53556","tid":2244104,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4f9f206f3467abfca6bbf1042c7aab31539f954","tid":224410